{"tid":2337622,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"全球最賺錢YouTuber竟年僅9歲　年收入賺達2950萬美元","createTime":"2020-12-23T12:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T17:29:06.000Z","uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1d7fc8d0733111ed776ee24833a6667e65b503d1","tid":2337622,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20201219134804-3adebda3978fcce1dff2cb7e2d29d2a3-mobile.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20201219134804-3adebda3978fcce1dff2cb7e2d29d2a3-mobile.jpg&h=fabf42cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n商業雜誌《富比士》（Forbes）18日公布2020年全世界最賺錢YouTuber，再度是這位美國德州的小網紅萊恩（Ryan KaJi）拔得頭籌，他蟬聯3屆冠軍，分享品牌玩具及遊戲，以及有趣的開箱文聞名，使小小年紀的他，年收入就賺進高達2950萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20201219134824-e63eb4651ca95406f280a1fe8c9fb9c1-tablet.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20201219134824-e63eb4651ca95406f280a1fe8c9fb9c1-tablet.png&h=d3117bde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《衛報》報導，萊恩賺進2950萬美元，收入來源主要是YouTube主頻道「萊恩的世界」（Ryan's World），他甚至與尼克兒童頻道簽約有一筆未公開交易，可能價值數百萬美元，還有其他品牌玩具和服飾分享達2億美元收入，例如與瑪莎百貨（Marks&amp;Spencer）合作的品牌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20201219134956-ee18835f8350f4d2d441b4fe81f0a9d5-tablet.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20201219134956-ee18835f8350f4d2d441b4fe81f0a9d5-tablet.png&h=9333bcfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n萊恩於2015年3月開啟了Youtuber生涯，而這個契機，是多年前觀看其他玩具評論時，萊恩問媽媽「其他孩子都在YouTube上，我怎麼沒有在YouTube上？」幸運的是，他的父母也經常支持著他，萊恩甚至被稱作「兒童影響者」，自開播以來，拓展出９個頻道，已累計達4170萬人訂閱，總觀看數達122億。"},{"pid":"5a3d785d122a939c19f075420b3880168beaee25","tid":2337622,"uid":148438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/l